{
  "texts": [
    "EU-Net [31] is an enhanced U-Net framework that enhances semantic information and introduces an adaptive global context module to extract key features.",
    "MSNet [9] designs a subtraction unit to generate difference features between adjacent layers and pyramidically equips it with different receptive fields to capture multi-scale information.",
    "In addition, it introduces LossNet to supervise the perceptual features at each layer.",
    "Net [71] utilizes an improved U-Net in the merging phase and embeds new location feature information.",
    "Thanks to the rich knowledge of positional information and concatenated features, this model achieves higher accuracy and universality in polyp segmentation.Transformer-based methods."
  ]
}